<div id="outline-container-orgheadline3" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgheadline3"><span class="section-number-2">3</span> My most recent work</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-3">
<p>
<b>Classical Planning in Deep Latent Space: From Unlabelled Images to PDDL (and Back)</b>
</p>

<div class="container-fluid">
<div class="row-fluid">
<div class="span6">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>The first and successful attempt to generate the symbolic input for Classical Planner directly from images</li>

<li>Generate symbols using Variational AutoEncoder w/ gumbel-softmax (ICLR17)</li>

<li>Then solve the symbolic planning problem</li>

<li>Map the results back to images</li>
</ul>

</div>
<div class="span6">

<div class="figure">
<p><img src="img/results/mnist-plan.png" alt="mnist-plan.png" />
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Been through reviewed workshops (KEPS17 in ICAPS, NeSy17, Cognitum17 in IJCAI)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

